{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01ViGJV6UUSgsCoh5XUaPhxG","type":"tool_result","content":"     1вҶ’# Title Extractor Architecture\n     2вҶ’\n     3вҶ’## Pipeline Overview\n     4вҶ’\n     5вҶ’The title extractor (`lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`) takes raw OCR text from recipe photos and identifies recipe titles using a multi-stage pipeline combining structural heuristics and semantic embeddings.\n     6вҶ’\n     7вҶ’```\n     8вҶ’                          RAW OCR TEXT\n     9вҶ’                              |\n    10вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    11вҶ’                    |   Split into lines  |\n    12вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    13вҶ’                              |\n    14вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    15вҶ’                    |  Skip garbled burst |  findBurstEnd(): discard leading\n    16вҶ’                    |  (short OCR noise)  |  short lines with bad vowel ratios\n    17вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    18вҶ’                              |\n    19вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    20вҶ’                    |  Pre-merge          |  Lines starting with /&+:( are\n    21вҶ’                    |  continuation lines |  joined to preceding line\n    22вҶ’                    +--------------------+    e.g. \"SAFFRON BUNS\" + \"/ VARIATION\"\n    23вҶ’                              |               -> \"SAFFRON BUNS / VARIATION\"\n    24вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    25вҶ’                    |  Generate candidates|  For each line: single, 2-line join,\n    26вҶ’                    |  (single + joins)   |  3-line join. Dedup by normalized text.\n    27вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    28вҶ’                              |\n    29вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    30вҶ’                    |  Hard filters       |  9 independent checks per candidate\n    31вҶ’                    |  (reject non-titles)|  (see detail below)\n    32вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    33вҶ’                              |\n    34вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    35вҶ’                    |  Cap at 25          |  Prefer ALL_CAPS + short candidates\n    36вҶ’                    |  (pre-filter)       |  to limit embedding API calls\n    37вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    38вҶ’                              |\n    39вҶ’              ================v=================\n    40вҶ’              |     EMBEDDING SCORING            |\n    41вҶ’              |                                  |\n    42вҶ’              |  +---------v----------+          |\n    43вҶ’              |  | Pass 1: rawScore   |          |\n    44вҶ’              |  | titleSim - max(    |          |\n    45вҶ’              |  |  headerSim,        |          |\n    46вҶ’              |  |  noiseSim)         |          |\n    47вҶ’              |  +--------------------+          |\n    48вҶ’              |            |                     |\n    49вҶ’              |  +---------v----------+          |\n    50вҶ’              |  | Structural heading  |         |\n    51вҶ’              |  | selection           |         |\n    52вҶ’              |  | (best ALL_CAPS by   |         |\n    53вҶ’              |  |  embedding quality) |         |\n    54вҶ’              |  +--------------------+          |\n    55вҶ’              |            |                     |\n    56вҶ’              |  +---------v----------+          |\n    57вҶ’              |  | OCR truncation      |         |\n    58вҶ’              |  | penalty (-1.0)      |         |\n    59вҶ’              |  | \"FRON\" vs \"SAFFRON\" |         |\n    60вҶ’              |  +--------------------+          |\n    61вҶ’              |            |                     |\n    62вҶ’              |  +---------v----------+          |\n    63вҶ’              |  | Pass 2: bonuses     |         |\n    64вҶ’              |  | position * 1.12     |         |\n    65вҶ’              |  | ALL_CAPS + 0.08     |         |\n    66вҶ’              |  | structural + 0.10   |         |\n    67вҶ’              |  +--------------------+          |\n    68вҶ’              |                                  |\n    69вҶ’              ==================================+\n    70вҶ’                              |\n    71вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    72вҶ’                    |  Bilingual          |  Suppress ALL_CAPS translation at\n    73вҶ’                    |  detection          |  pos 1-2 if cosine > 0.4 with\n    74вҶ’                    |  (pre-threshold)    |  mixed-case title at pos 0\n    75вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    76вҶ’                              |\n    77вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    78вҶ’                    |  Threshold filter   |  max(0.08, bestThresholdScore * 0.7)\n    79вҶ’                    |                     |  Empty-pool fallback: if nothing\n    80вҶ’                    |                     |  survives, take best positional\n    81вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    82вҶ’                              |\n    83вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    84вҶ’                    |  Post-threshold     |\n    85вҶ’                    |  cleanup            |\n    86вҶ’                    |  - prefix removal   |  Remove \"ARAYES\" when \"ARAYES SHRAK\" present\n    87вҶ’                    |  - join protection  |  Keep continuation joins, drop fragments\n    88вҶ’                    |  - sub-section      |  Remove ALL_CAPS headers followed by\n    89вҶ’                    |    removal          |  ingredients when longer parent exists\n    90вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n    91вҶ’                              |\n    92вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    93вҶ’                    |  Dedup              |  Shorter substring wins\n    94вҶ’                    |  (substring-based)  |  \"Pierogi Ruskie\" beats\n    95вҶ’                    +--------------------+  \"Pierogi Ruskie 200g maki\"\n    96вҶ’                              |\n    97вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n    98вҶ’                    |  Multi-title guard  |  2+ ALL_CAPS -> check ingredient gaps\n    99вҶ’                    |                     |  1 ALL_CAPS -> highest score wins\n   100вҶ’                    |                     |  0 ALL_CAPS -> keep all\n   101вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n   102вҶ’                              |\n   103вҶ’                    +---------v----------+\n   104вҶ’                    |  Sort by position,  |\n   105вҶ’                    |  cap at 3, join     |\n   106вҶ’                    |  with \" + \"         |\n   107вҶ’                    +--------------------+\n   108вҶ’                              |\n   109вҶ’                        EXTRACTED TITLE\n   110вҶ’```\n   111вҶ’\n   112вҶ’## Hard Filters Detail\n   113вҶ’\n   114вҶ’`passesHardFilters()` applies 9 independent checks. A candidate is rejected if **any** check fails:\n   115вҶ’\n   116вҶ’| # | Filter | Example rejected |\n   117вҶ’|---|--------|-----------------|\n   118вҶ’| 1 | Length 3-80 chars | `\"A\"`, very long body text |\n   119вҶ’| 2 | Ingredient detection | `\"2 cups flour\"`, `\"100g masla\"`, `\"do smaku\"` |\n   120вҶ’| 3 | Leading number | `\"1. Preheat oven\"`, `\"- 2 jajka\"` |\n   121вҶ’| 4 | Metadata patterns | `\"SERVES 4\"`, `\"NA 3 PAPRYKI\"`, `\"30 MIN\"` |\n   122вҶ’| 5 | OCR garble | Low vowel ratio, lowercase-start, mid-sentence boundary |\n   123вҶ’| 6 | Pipe separator | `\"Lato \\| Dania glowne\"` (chapter header) |\n   124вҶ’| 7 | Bullet line | `\"- flour\"`, `\"* sugar\"` |\n   125вҶ’| 8 | Section label | `\"INGREDIENTS\"`, `\"SKLADNIKI\"`, `\"Przygotowanie\"` |\n   126вҶ’| 9 | Non-title single word | `\"the\"`, `\"and\"`, `\"buns\"`, `\"with\"` |\n   127вҶ’\n   128вҶ’## Scoring Model\n   129вҶ’\n   130вҶ’Each candidate receives a composite score built from three signals:\n   131вҶ’\n   132вҶ’```\n   133вҶ’rawScore = cosineSim(candidate, TITLE_REF) - max(\n   134вҶ’             cosineSim(candidate, HEADER_REF),\n   135вҶ’             cosineSim(candidate, NOISE_REF)\n   136вҶ’           )\n   137вҶ’\n   138вҶ’score = rawScore * positionFactor + allCapsBonus + structuralBonus\n   139вҶ’```\n   140вҶ’\n   141вҶ’**Reference embeddings** (cached across calls):\n   142вҶ’- `TITLE_REF`: \"recipe name, dish title, name of the food, nazwa przepisu, nazwa dania\"\n   143вҶ’- `HEADER_REF`: \"ingredients list, cooking directions, section heading, skladniki, przygotowanie\"\n   144вҶ’- `NOISE_REF`: \"page number, table of contents, book footer, garbled text\"\n   145вҶ’\n   146вҶ’**Bonuses:**\n   147вҶ’\n   148вҶ’| Bonus | Value | Condition |\n   149вҶ’|-------|-------|-----------|\n   150вҶ’| Position factor | x1.0 to x1.12 (multiplicative) | Top-half of document, linear decay |\n   151вҶ’| ALL_CAPS | +0.08 (additive) | All letters uppercase, >= 4 alpha chars |\n   152вҶ’| Structural heading | +0.10 (additive) | Best ALL_CAPS heading by embedding quality |\n   153вҶ’\n   154вҶ’The `thresholdScore` deliberately excludes the structural bonus to prevent it from inflating the cutoff on multi-recipe pages.\n   155вҶ’\n   156вҶ’## Key Design Decisions\n   157вҶ’\n   158вҶ’**Multiplicative position bonus**: Additive position bonuses let garbled early text dominate. Multiplicative amplifies existing quality without creating it.\n   159вҶ’\n   160вҶ’**Pre-merge over downstream join protection**: Continuation lines (`/&+:`) are merged upstream in `buildCandidates` so the complete title enters the pool as a single candidate. This replaced 5 iterations of fragile downstream join-survival logic.\n   161вҶ’\n   162вҶ’**Pre-threshold bilingual detection**: Must run before threshold computation. Otherwise the ALL_CAPS translation inflates the threshold beyond the mixed-case primary title's reach (chicken-and-egg problem).\n   163вҶ’\n   164вҶ’**Shorter-wins dedup**: The dedup rule is intentionally simple (\"shorter substring wins\") because upstream filters (prefix removal, sub-section removal) ensure conflicting shorter fragments are removed before dedup runs. This has been incorrectly \"improved\" 5 times by the automated loop.\n   165вҶ’\n   166вҶ’## Language Support\n   167вҶ’\n   168вҶ’The extractor handles both English and Polish recipes:\n   169вҶ’- Measurement units: `lyЕјka`, `szklanka`, `szczypta`, `garsc`\n   170вҶ’- Metadata: `NA 3 PAPRYKI`, `DLA 4 OSOB`, `N MIN`, `N GODZ`\n   171вҶ’- Section labels: `SKLADNIKI`, `PRZYGOTOWANIE`, `SPOSOB WYKONANIA`\n   172вҶ’- OCR garble: Polish vowels (`Д…ДҷГі`) included in vowel ratio check\n   173вҶ’- Common prepositions: `w`, `z` allowed in multi-word garble detection\n   174вҶ’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014867ti9qiG3i71fZNmJ1wr","session_id":"170bdbf7-3568-4ea7-9b3d-3d7e36d78c47","uuid":"fd483a9b-b52c-43c3-8bcd-dd43f36cc173"}
