{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012t2kfFVkGF88UnmaxNMvr1","type":"tool_result","content":"     1вҶ’# Iteration 17 вҖ” Failure Analysis\n     2вҶ’\n     3вҶ’## Failing case\n     4вҶ’\n     5вҶ’- **File:** `Faszerowana papryka.real.txt`\n     6вҶ’- **Expected:** `Faszerowana papryka`\n     7вҶ’- **Got:** `WARZYWA`\n     8вҶ’\n     9вҶ’---\n    10вҶ’\n    11вҶ’## Document structure\n    12вҶ’\n    13вҶ’```\n    14вҶ’Line  0: Faszerowana papryka          вҶҗ correct title (mixed-case)\n    15вҶ’Line  1: PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM          вҶҗ ALL_CAPS romanization\n    16вҶ’Line  2: нҢҢн”„лҰ¬м№ҙ кі„лһҖм°ң                вҶҗ Korean script\n    17вҶ’Line  3: Ten bardzo prosty przepisвҖҰ   вҶҗ body text\n    18вҶ’Line  5: NA 3 PAPRYKI                 вҶҗ serving-size metadata (filtered вң“)\n    19вҶ’Line  6: Przygotowanie                вҶҗ section label (filtered вң“)\n    20вҶ’Line  7: 10 minut                     вҶҗ time (filtered by startsWithNumber вң“)\n    21вҶ’Line  8: Pieczenie 30 minut           вҶҗ time line (passes hard filters!)\n    22вҶ’Line  9: SKЕҒADNIKI                    вҶҗ section label (filtered вң“)\n    23вҶ’Lines 10вҖ“17: ingredients\n    24вҶ’Lines 18вҖ“24: instructions (body text)\n    25вҶ’Line 25: WARZYWA                      вҶҗ chapter/category footer, wrong pick\n    26вҶ’```\n    27вҶ’\n    28вҶ’---\n    29вҶ’\n    30вҶ’## Why the failure occurs вҖ” step by step\n    31вҶ’\n    32вҶ’### Step 1 вҖ” Bilingual detection fires on `PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM`\n    33вҶ’\n    34вҶ’`Faszerowana papryka` is a mixed-case candidate at position 0. `PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM` is ALL_CAPS at position 1. The layout-based bilingual detector (Method 2) fires:\n    35вҶ’\n    36вҶ’- `prePos0` = `Faszerowana papryka` (вүҘ2 words, not ALL_CAPS) вң“\n    37вҶ’- `nearbyAllCaps` includes `PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM` at position 1\n    38вҶ’- `pos0Words` = `{\"faszerowana\", \"papryka\"}` вҖ” no words shared with `[\"paprika\", \"gyeran-jjim\"]`\n    39вҶ’вҶ’ `PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM` is classified as a translation candidate and suppressed.\n    40вҶ’\n    41вҶ’This part is **correct** behaviour. The title and its romanization are different words in different scripts.\n    42вҶ’\n    43вҶ’### Step 2 вҖ” `firstStructuralHeading` becomes `undefined`\n    44вҶ’\n    45вҶ’`PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM` was the only structural heading (ALL_CAPS, вүҘ2 words, every significant word вүҘ4 letters). After it is identified as a translation in Fix 2, `nonTranslationStructural` is empty, so `firstStructuralHeading = undefined`. No candidate receives the structural bonus (+0.10).\n    46вҶ’\n    47вҶ’### Step 3 вҖ” `WARZYWA` passes all hard filters\n    48вҶ’\n    49вҶ’`WARZYWA` (Polish: \"vegetables\") is a chapter/category footer on the last line. It passes every hard filter:\n    50вҶ’\n    51вҶ’- Length 7 вҖ” between 3 and 80 вң“\n    52вҶ’- Not an ingredient вң“\n    53вҶ’- Does not start with a digit вң“\n    54вҶ’- Not in METADATA_PATTERNS вң“\n    55вҶ’- `isLikelyGarbled` вҖ” 7 letters, vowel ratio 3/7 вүҲ 0.43 (within range), single word but 7 chars (> 3 threshold) вң“\n    56вҶ’- **Not in SECTION_LABELS** вң“ вҶҗ the root miss; \"warzywa\" is not listed\n    57вҶ’\n    58вҶ’Because it is ALL_CAPS, it earns `allCapsBonus = 0.08`.\n    59вҶ’\n    60вҶ’### Step 4 вҖ” Multi-title guard collapses to `WARZYWA`\n    61вҶ’\n    62вҶ’Both `Faszerowana papryka` and `WARZYWA` survive the threshold filter. At the multi-title guard:\n    63вҶ’\n    64вҶ’```\n    65вҶ’allCapsSelected = [WARZYWA]   вҶҗ exactly 1 ALL_CAPS survivor\n    66вҶ’вҶ’ selected = [highest scorer]\n    67вҶ’```\n    68вҶ’\n    69вҶ’`WARZYWA` wins because:\n    70вҶ’- Its `allCapsBonus` (+0.08) elevates its score above `Faszerowana papryka`, which receives no bonus.\n    71вҶ’- `WARZYWA` is at the end of the document (relativePosition вүҲ 1.0), so `positionFactor = 1.0` вҖ” no penalty for late position.\n    72вҶ’- `Faszerowana papryka` gets a mild position bonus (relativePosition 0 вҶ’ positionFactor вүҲ 1.12), but `rawScore Г— 0.12` is less than +0.08 if the embedding scores are close or if WARZYWA's rawScore is comparable.\n    73вҶ’\n    74вҶ’---\n    75вҶ’\n    76вҶ’## Root cause\n    77вҶ’\n    78вҶ’### 1. `SECTION_LABELS` does not cover Polish chapter/category labels\n    79вҶ’\n    80вҶ’\"WARZYWA\" (vegetables), and likely similar terms like \"MIДҳSO\" (meat), \"RYBY\" (fish), \"DESERY\" (desserts), \"ZUPY\" (soups), etc., are common recipe-book chapter headers that appear as ALL_CAPS single-word footers or section dividers. They are not recipe titles. The set currently omits this entire category of labels.\n    81вҶ’\n    82вҶ’### 2. The multi-title guard's \"single ALL_CAPS вҶ’ collapse to highest score\" heuristic is positionally blind\n    83вҶ’\n    84вҶ’When exactly one ALL_CAPS candidate survives alongside mixed-case candidates, the guard unconditionally collapses to the highest scorer. This conflates two distinct situations:\n    85вҶ’- The ALL_CAPS is the real title (e.g., `KREM SELEROWY Z GORGONZOLA`) вҖ” collapse is correct.\n    86вҶ’- The ALL_CAPS is a section/chapter label that happened to score marginally higher вҖ” collapse is wrong.\n    87вҶ’\n    88вҶ’The guard does not check whether the ALL_CAPS candidate appears *after* all the recipe content (ingredients, instructions), which would be a strong signal it is a footer/category label rather than a title.\n    89вҶ’\n    90вҶ’### 3. The `allCapsBonus` is unconditional for single-word terms\n    91вҶ’\n    92вҶ’Single ALL_CAPS words like `WARZYWA` receive the full +0.08 bonus even though `isStructuralHeading` requires вүҘ2 words for the structural heading slot. The bonus amplifies a weak candidate without the safety check that applies to the structural heading pathway.\n    93вҶ’\n    94вҶ’---\n    95вҶ’\n    96вҶ’## Common theme\n    97вҶ’\n    98вҶ’All three issues share the same underlying failure mode: **an ALL_CAPS bonus system designed to prefer recipe titles inadvertently elevates vocabulary-category labels** (chapter headings, section markers, footers) that are structurally indistinguishable from titles under the current filters. The document's actual title вҖ” clearly present on line 0 with strong positional evidence вҖ” is bypassed because the algorithm's ALL_CAPS preference is not guarded against labels that appear after the body content.\n    99вҶ’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014867ti9qiG3i71fZNmJ1wr","session_id":"170bdbf7-3568-4ea7-9b3d-3d7e36d78c47","uuid":"8d15933d-3f5d-402a-aea9-f3a5c74f1e8e"}
